<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= title %> | Privacy Policy</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="<%= links.icon %>" type="image/x-icon" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />
  </head>
  <body
    class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 min-h-screen text-white"
  >
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-md">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We may collect personal information such as your Discord username and
          ID when you use our bot.
        </p>
        <br />
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">
          2. How We Use Your Information
        </h2>
        <p>
          The information we collect is used to improve the bot's functionality
          and user experience.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information.
          However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely
          secure.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties
          without your consent.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update our privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be
          reflected on this page.
        </p>
        <br />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us
          through our Discord server.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  </body>
</html>
